rs232

RS232 is serial communication protocol.
This code is intended to handle serial communication within C++ class.

additional library needed:
* CImg for comand line option, only.
  Please, install CImg parent folder as CImg

install example
  cd code
  #RS232
  git clone git://github.com/coupdair/rs232.git
  cd rs232; ls
  cd ..
  #CImg
  wget http://downloads.sourceforge.net/project/cimg/CImg-1.4.9.zip?r=http%3A%2F%2Fsourceforge.net%2Fprojects%2Fcimg%2Ffiles%2F&ts=1337853554&use_mirror=switch
  unzip CImg-1.4.9.zip
  ln -s CImg-1.4.9 CImg
  ls CImg
  #RS232
  cd rs232
  make

